WEBVTT

1
00:46:23.040 --> 00:46:24.070 
准将
Commodore.

2
00:46:24.140 --> 00:46:27.040 
长官 他们抢走了无畏号
LT. GlLLETTE: Sir, they've taken the Dauntless!

3
00:46:28.510 --> 00:46:30.240 
准将!
Commodore!

4
00:46:30.310 --> 00:46:32.810 
他们把船抢走了!
They've taken the ship!

5
00:46:32.880 --> 00:46:35.110 
斯派洛和特纳把无畏号抢走了!
Sparrow and Turner have taken the Dauntless!

6
00:46:35.190 --> 00:46:39.050 
特纳 你太鲁莽了
Rash, Turner. Too rash.

7
00:46:39.860 --> 00:46:44.690 
毫无疑问他是我见过的最难缠的海盗
That is without doubt the worst pirate I have ever seen.

8
00:46:47.170 --> 00:46:48.690 
他们来了
Here they come.

9
00:46:53.340 --> 00:46:56.700 
转舵! 转舵!
Bring her around! Bring her around!

